Milestone 1:

* Terminal emulator
    - window handling
        . Resize
    - cursor
    - clip board
    - Ctrl-C

* Execute command
    - read back stderr

* Cmdline Interpreter
    - glob
    - redirect output

* Usability
    - color
    - tab completion

* Builtin commands
    - exit
    - cd

* Cross platform
    - windows support

Milestone 2:

* Interactive commands
    - Use pty on unix to support more complicated console programs (sqlite, gdb, ...)
    - On windows msdn: 'CreatePseudoConsole'

